    "| Clustering | Do results include segments representing structurally constrained communities? |\n",
    "| Labelling | Would a member of this cluster feel fairly described? |\n",
    "| Recommendations | Does this recommendation provide support before asking for behaviour change? |\n",
    "| Impact brief | Can a non-technical community member understand, challenge, and act on this? |"
